The iPhone 12 Pro Max specs are revealed. Several months before the September keynote, a leak came to lift the veil on part of the technical sheet of the smartphone. This year, Apple has reportedly decided to incorporate a 64-megapixel photo sensor on the back and a large 4,400 mAh battery. In the process, we discover a design almost unchanged from the iPhone 11 Pro Max.⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
